"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"  Since the outbreak of the new coronavirus, our lives have been challenged once again. In order to have a healthy body and avoid viruses, Let’s do something. The following suggestions are which I think can improve immunity hopefully,come and join with me.\\n\\n**Clean up the intestinal environment** \\n\\n  Our digestive system is the place where viruses are most likely to attack, and it is also the place with the most immune cells.  So it’s imporant to keep our intestinal clean.\\n\\n  Do:eat foods rich in dietary fiber and fermented\\n\\n  Do not:insufficient sleep and excessive stress. \\n\\n**A balanced diet Eating** \\n\\n  A balanced diet and eating 80% full is a very important eating habit. You can eat more vegetables rich in vitamins A, C, E and high-quality protein foods. Try not to touch high-calorie, high-salt things, because this may promote inflammation. \\n\\n**Moderate exercise**\\n\\n  Moderate exercise can promote the flow of immune cells throughout the body and help to detect the presence of the virus as soon as possible. \\n\\n  Develop the habit of moderate exercise \\n\\n  Climb stairs instead of elevators\\n\\n  Walk often\\n\\n**High quality sleep** \\n\\n  Lack of sleep can lead to a decline in immunity, so it’s important to maintain a good sleep. In addition, hormones that are secreted only at night are very helpful for improving immunity, so it’s necessary to maintain a regular schedule of work and rest.    \\n\\n  Get enough sleep\\n\\n  Maintain a regular schedule\\n\\n  take a sunbathe when you get up\\n\\n**Take a bath** \\n\\n Hot bath seems to have nothing to do with improving immunity, but bathing can relax people's body and mind, relieve fatigue, and help sleep. In addition, people’s body temperature will rise during hot baths, speed up blood flow, which can promote immunity Cell circulation, which is also good for improving immunity. \\n\\nTake a bath 1-2 hours before going to bed\\n\\nKeep the water temperature around 38-40 degrees, soak for 15-20 minutes \\n\\nIf you don’t have the conditions to take a bath, it’s okay to soak your feet \\n\\n**Keep a happy mood** \\n\\nStudies have shown that laughing is very helpful for improving immunity. \\n\\nWatch funny variety shows, movies, and animations,\\n\\nsmile consciously. \\n\\n**Release one's pressure**\\n\\n Excessive stress is the main reason for the decline in immunity. But it is impossible to have no pressure at all, so we have to learn how to release our pressure and minimize the damage.\\n\\n Relax\\n\\nTalk with your good friend, \\n\\nTake a deep breath,\\n\\n Listen to music.\",\"timestamp\":1638510354,\"title\":\"How to keep healthy:7 habits\"},\"digest\":\"skqUxAFk9RLLdYhcyaKvkSi8TwraTQgBUCHjYo_KESQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x1C97Ee9018C3554476dd99A4FA3f811B503E6DDe\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MpXTeUjTVdpCu7w8rkUZBC_V7ZIzFKCRnw5wPY1qxWo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"uuBg6WH57S4RXI5pTU5pB47aB4FVkC2_Dw7AU9fvoeg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ZApHwfCjoE1zskgyjV81ANDoZc_p00qG8pymiwloUxqJlw2uyB-PDLSuCFgSWopmPCNp4VJccskdSYbeVjFZew\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x258a4aab7bdb42ea995b7f752a319e4f76098d577efe247c118b9f661ab068b4633ee023811134a54a828eb4a46d44b1d2efefcf1e2a12cfe83096aff957b6a01c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MpXTeUjTVdpCu7w8rkUZBC_V7ZIzFKCRnw5wPY1qxWo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"uuBg6WH57S4RXI5pTU5pB47aB4FVkC2_Dw7AU9fvoeg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"skqUxAFk9RLLdYhcyaKvkSi8TwraTQgBUCHjYo_KESQ\"}"